Package Blackjack.Exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BetTooBigException
    Thrown when a bet exceeds amount of money available.
    DeckEmptyException
    Thrown when the deck is empty and some action is trying to be performed on the deck.
    HandBiggerThanDeckException
    Thrown when a hand is bigger than the deck being drawn from.
    InvalidBetException
    Thrown when a bet is entered that isn't more than 0.
    NegativeMoneyException
    Thrown when a negative amount of money is reached, which is an invalid state.
